{'en': {'shortDesc': 'graphical user interface for Zeitgeist', 'pkgName': 'gnome-activity-journal', 'longDesc': u"Zeitgeist is a service which logs the user's activities and events (files opened, websites visited, conversations hold with other people, etc.) and makes the relevant information available to other applications.\n\nIt serves as a comprehensive activity log and also makes it possible to determine relationships between items based on usage patterns.\n\nThis package contains the GNOME Activity Journal, a graphical user interface which shows a journal of your activities."}}